ubx_message.name: UBX-MGA-BDS-ALM
ubx_message.description: BeiDou almanac assistance. This message allows the delivery of BeiDou almanac assistance to a receiver. See section AssistNow online in the integration manual for details.

payload_fields.name: deltaI
payload_fields.description: Almanac correction of orbit reference inclination at reference time

payload_fields.name: sqrtA
payload_fields.description: Almanac square root of semi-major axis

payload_fields.name: M0
payload_fields.description: Almanac mean anomaly at reference time

payload_fields.name: Omega0
payload_fields.description: Almanac longitude of ascending node of orbit plane at computed according to reference time
